  overviewExtra="Many patients come to Thrive Dental having skipped dental visits for years — and are relieved to find that a thorough exam and cleaning is often all they need to get back on track. We see patients from across Bayside, Flushing, Whitestone, and Fresh Meadows who've been told elsewhere that they need extensive treatment, and a preventive-first approach resolves most issues before they become costly. Our general dental exams cover more than a cleaning: every visit includes a temporomandibular joint (TMJ) check, gum tissue assessment, condition of any existing crowns or fillings, bite evaluation, and a genuine conversation about anything you've noticed between visits. We treat every member of the family — from a child's first checkup to adults managing long-term oral health goals."
